The best most annoying anime i've ever seen.I fucking love it so much! The first season was the most romantic thing i've ever seen with Raku X Kosaki being so akward because they liked each other it was kinda realistic.Most anoying thing as i stated is how obvious it is that they like each other.JUST MAKE THE FUCKING MOVE RAKU YOU STUPID FAGGOT! don't make the girl do the work. Huhhh the timings in this where the worst especially the baseball going through the window when Kosaki was about to ask out Raku..it was so fustrating. My favorite and intense part was when Raku waspicking the number for the walk...IT WAS the most intense thing i ever fucking saw holy shit.I love this anime sad that the ending of the manga is so sad and disappointing for the Raku X Kosaki fans. I would really love to see the anime have two different endings a Chitoge ending and Kosaki ending instead of it just fucking coping shit of the mange.I think the anime should have some originality so people can buy it for a certain part..like the multiple endings part i mentioned.Anyway if you liked oregairu then this is the next thing for you \n
10/10
